articles.title: The Judgment Day Officially Adds Fifth Member On WWE Raw - Wrestling Inc.
articles.description: On behalf of The Judgment Day, Damian Priest officially welcomed a new member to the group, bringing its membership to a total of five ahead of Survivor Series.
